                        "italic": true
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "text": "The sculk is not growing randomly. It is growing in patterns. If you map the sculk veins of the deep dark, they form a shape. The shape is a circle. The circle is getting smaller.",
                        "color": "dark_gray",
                        "italic": true
                      }
                    ],
                    [
                      {
                        "text": "At the center of the circle, buried deeper than anyone has dug, the portal waits. It is patient. It has always been patient.",
